Permission: com.google.android.c2dm.permission.SEND
[android:exported=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: A Broadcast Receiver is found to be shared with other apps on the device therefore leaving it accessible to any other application on the device. It is protected by a permission which is not defined in the analysed application. As a result, the protection level of the permission should be checked where it is defined. If it is set to normal or dangerous, a malicious application can request and obtain the permission and interact with the component. If it is set to signature, only applications signed with the same certificate can obtain the permission.

FCS_RBG_EXT.2.1,FCS_RBG_EXT.2.2.choice: The application perform all deterministic random bit generation (DRBG) services in accordance with NIST Special Publication 800-90A using Hash_DRBG. FCS_COP.1.1(2).choice: The application perform cryptographic hashing services not in accordance with FCS_COP.1.1(2) and uses the cryptographic algorithm RC2/RC4/MD4/MD5.

FCS_COP.1.1(3).choice: The application perform cryptographic signature services (generation and verification) in accordance with a specified cryptographic algorithm RSA schemes using cryptographic key sizes of 2048-bit or greater.

playstore_details.description:
Read the latest news related to the cryptocurrency and blockchain world - first at BitGarage.

BitGarage is a news app dedicated to cryptocurrency, and blockchain news. Find here the best-curated articles on Bitcoin, Ripple, Litecoin, OMG, and other cryptocurrencies. With just one click, read the summarized version of your favorite crypto news.  

We present only facts and no opinions. Our aim is to make useful information reach every people of the country. Every people must get useful information from credible sources and use that information to progress in digital and virtual currency sector. 

Bit Garage is a non-profit initiative to strengthen and support the digital and virtual currency of our country. We hope we will get your precious support in this initiative.
